snippet.title: Acroamatic Abatement | 14.0 Teaser | SCP: Secret Laboratory
snippet.description:
Site-02 houses several anomalies which need cleaning up after. Ever wondered who does the dirty work? 

Play the game for free: https://store.steampowered.com/app/700330/SCP_Secret_Laboratory/
Patreon page: https://patreon.scpslgame.com
Webpage: http://scpslgame.com

Credits:
- Professor Rigel Keane (Voiceover) by Nick "Greekas" Gikas (https://nickgikasvo.com)
- Writing, editing, and coordination by x3j50
- Assisted by Spooky, and Tamer
- Level design by Tosmatosoup
- Music "Acroamatic Abatement" by Sixxy

This video is licensed under the CC-BY-SA 4.0 - https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

You are free to use this video in productions that are strongly related to SCP: Secret Laboratory (such as gameplay videos, reviews of the game, cinematics) without the need to credit us. In any other cases, you should do so in any meaningful way; for YouTube productions - description works just fine. For example: "The content includes work by Northwood for SCP: Secret Laboratory".

Based on “Acroamatic Abatement” by “HarryBlank”: 
https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/acroamatic-abatement
